♪As dusk approaches, dreams unfold♪

104
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:24,180
♪Laughter drifts with the wind,
hard to hold♪

105
00:08:24,180 --> 00:08:28,060
♪Entwined within the mortal world♪

106
00:08:28,060 --> 00:08:31,580
♪Watching fates intertwine, unfurled♪

107
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:38,740
♪Like moths chasing flames,
to blaze they're drawn♪

108
00:08:38,740 --> 00:08:42,940
♪We brave the darkness,
spiraling into cocoons♪

109
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:46,460
♪Chasing a single, unwavering dream♪

110
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:50,220
♪But life's endless twists and turns
can't be undone♪

111
00:08:50,220 --> 00:08:53,940
♪As fleeting splendor fades
without regret♪

112
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:57,820
♪We cross the smoke and ashes,
torn by goodbyes♪

113
00:08:57,862 --> 00:09:00,889
♪In every moment♪

114
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,480
Let's leave together.

115
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,560
Go to a place

116
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,760
where it's just the two of us.

117
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,080
All right.

118
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,560
From now on,

119
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,560
no more hatred.

120
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,440
Just us.

121
00:09:53,780 --> 00:10:00,060
♪When I first saw you,
my heart lost its guard♪

122
00:10:00,700 --> 00:10:08,260
♪I dreamed of our future,
at every dawn and dusk♪

123
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:16,540
♪Owe you an embrace,
wandered alone for so long♪

124
